OL,3,CHow big a health hazard is mould
OL,4,Cgrowing in London Underground stations?
OL,6,FAn investigation by ITV News London
OL,7,Fhas uncovered a health risk found in
OL,8,Fhomes has also been discovered on the
OL,9,Funderground.
OL,11,FBlack mould, which thrives in damp
OL,12,Fconditions, has spread through part of
OL,13,Fa busy station in West London.
OL,15,FThousands of Londoners walk just
OL,16,Finches from it each day at Shepherd's
OL,17,FBush and some told us they are worried
OL,18,Fabout the impact on their well-being.
