OL,3,CHow big a health hazard is mould
OL,4,Cgrowing in London Underground stations?
OL,6,FArmed with special testing equipment
OL,7,Fwe took a scientist for an expert
OL,8,Fopinion on the potential danger to
OL,9,FLondoners. He said it was "as bad as
OL,10,Fit can get".
OL,12,FWhat we found doesn't pose an
OL,13,Fimmediate danger to commuters but it's
OL,14,Funsightly, unpleasant and Transport
OL,15,Ffor London is taking action to get it
OL,16,Fcleaned up.
