OL,3,CHow big a health hazard is mould
OL,4,Cgrowing in London Underground stations?
OL,6,F"But having that as the list of the
OL,7,Fmany things that they have to keep
OL,8,Ftrack of in terms of maintenance seems
OL,9,Flike a good idea to me."
OL,11,FSince revealing the findings to
OL,12,FTransport for London a spokesperson
OL,13,Ftold us they are now aware of mould at
OL,14,FShepherd's Bush.
OL,16,FA statement added: "We are treating
OL,17,Fthe area with detergent and anti-mould
OL,18,Fcleaning products."
